g.text: an effect contains a list of effectful operations, ∑;
each operation in ∑ takes a list of params p , where k is the length of the list;
a handler deals with ∑ + 1 , i.e all operations in ∑ and returning pure values;

text.tspan: internally, for each operation in ∑, a handler receives p and a continuation.

g.text: a handler may choose to call the continuation zero, one or many times.
